rows.label: tlk70000055_03_msg0001
rows.name:
I was surprised when I first came
to Iira.

rows.label: tlk70000055_03_msg0002
rows.name:
The food here is just so good! Even the
food served at this camp looks and
tastes great.

rows.label: tlk70000055_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I went to the storehouse to investigate
what ingredients and spices are used
here and had another shock!

rows.label: tlk70000055_03_msg0004
rows.name:
The idiot in charge of the storehouse
was filching snacks on the job.

rows.label: tlk70000055_03_msg0005
rows.name:
I apprehended him on the spot, but
apparently he does it all the time.
Noowl even laughed at me for it!

rows.label: tlk70000055_03_msg0006
rows.name:
Stealing from the army is considered a
big crime in Superbia. I guess things
are different here in Iira...
